<promed@promedmail.org>
[The Minnesota Department of Health website
<http://www.health.state.mn.us/> indicates that for at least 17 of the
cases _E. coli_ O157:H7 isolates have been identified, all with the same
genetic fingerprint (presumably by pulsed-field gel electrophoresis
analysis). - Mod.ES
